      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am beyond excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally pampered and kept in pristine condition\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. I've loved every mile in this beauty, but it's time for it to find a new home. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
